reviews.text:
I mixed 10mL of this and vaped it single coil, 450f-500f.&#xD;
I actually had really  high hopes for this, I love sweet guava at 4% but had never experienced it any higher. Nice and acidic, crisp even, but with all the sweet guava blasting my taste buds I can't really pick anything else out. It doesn't taste bad, it's just... very bold, not exactly my type of mix. I did not try with TFA VBIC  + FA Cream Fresh, maybe thats the key. &#xD;
Thanks for sharing.
